The paper deals with mechanism design, which is a subfield of game theory (cs.GT). It also involves optimization and decision-making algorithms (cs.DS), as well as mathematical analysis (cs.MA) and economic theory (cs.EC). The paper also mentions the use of information theory (cs.IT) in characterizing the optimal mechanism.
